Joker Club is the first NFT project of Partouche Multiverse, a Web3 subsidiary of Groupe Partouche, first casino operator in Europe.

Each holder obtains access to the full IP ownership of their Joker art, accompanied by physical utility in the most luxurious casinos, hotels and restaurants in Europe.
Visit www.jokerclub.io for more details.
